OL,5, Half of state-funded schools in England
OL,6, for children with special educational  
OL,7, needs and disabilities are             
OL,8, oversubscribed, BBC research has found.
OL,10,FSchools have converted portable cabins 
OL,11,Fand even cupboards into teaching spaces
OL,12,Fbecause of a lack of room. Head        
OL,13,Fteachers say this puts pressure on     
OL,14,Fstaff and makes pupils anxious.        
OL,16,FParents say the wait for places means  
OL,17,Ftheir children are missing education.  
OL,19,FThe Department for Education says it is
OL,20,Fspending #2.6bn on new places.         
